// sqlite3_column_decltype(stmt, i) — declared type-name of the source column
// from CREATE TABLE; NULL for expression columns.  Available only when built
// with SQLITE_ENABLE_COLUMN_METADATA.  Distinct from sqlite3_column_type which
// returns the *runtime* SQLITE_INTEGER/REAL/TEXT/BLOB/NULL of the bound row.
// Spec App E.C.
// =============================================================================

